{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_00_01","textHome":"我家的中华料理店，从父辈开始就快倒了……@可母亲和奶奶依旧每日挥霍无度……@但是，面对这样一家子总要有人能担起责任！@那么，我，由比鹤乃！@总有一天会成为成大事立大业的人！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":101}]}],"group_10":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_00_18","textHome":"好，完成了！右腿单立保持了24小时！@好漫长啊……说来，这个训练比起消耗体力，@更像是在与无聊做斗争啊。@不过，左腿也来练一下吧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":100}]}],"group_11":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":201,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_00_19","textHome":"还不够还不够还不够！……我还要变的更强！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":101}]}],"group_12":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_00_20","textHome":"嗯嗯，这样确实上了一个台阶！肯定没错！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":100}]}],"group_13":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_00_21","textHome":"听我说呀！我就稍微练了练拳脚，@旁边的野猫就摔得四脚朝天了！@没错……肯定是我变强了！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":100}]}],"group_14":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_00_22","textHome":"我做到啦！前阵子去动物园的时候，@我让狮子坐下了哟！就站在笼子前，@心里想着「坐下！」而已~！@我好像达到这种境界了呢"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"id":100300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300}]}],"group_15":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_00_23","textHome":"嗯？新闻？「海豚秀上海豚发飙了」？@啊，确实是我！我在观众席上想着@「要是跳得再卖力点不是很帅吗？」，@它们就感觉到了！虽然我也不懂是什么原理！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":8.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":100}]}],"group_16":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_52_24","textHome":"新年快乐，吃回锅肉！麻婆豆腐，过吉祥年！@……哼哼，这是在新年问候里宣传我家菜品@的行动哦！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":100300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":201}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":100}]}],"group_17":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_52_25","textHome":"早啊！气温有点低，虽然可以喝点面汤暖暖身@子，但还是跳绳吧！先跳上一个小时，开始@吧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":100300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"id":100300,"motion":201}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300}]}],"group_18":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_52_26","textHome":"偶尔视察敌情也是很重要的！所以，这街头的@大阪烧我就收下了！啊呜，嗯嗯……嗯，这@个很好吃！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.1,"chara":[{"id":100300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":8.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":100}]}],"group_19":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_52_27","textHome":"哇!?太阳都落山了啊。那今天的游玩就结束@了吧，把东西收拾收拾！然后……回三日月@庄去，继续玩吧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":100300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"id":100300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"id":100300,"motion":201}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300}]}],"group_2":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_00_03","textHome":"竟然是要和我谈心吗……没事没事！@我应该尝试各种事情！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":200}]}],"group_20":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_52_28","textHome":"初梦是哪天做的梦来着？元旦？还是第二天的@梦？嗯……算了，反正我都是睡得很熟的，@一点也记不起做了什么梦，啊哈哈……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"id":100300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":100300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":300}]}],"group_21":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_52_29","textHome":"嗯——好嘞，结束了！只要最强的我动起手来@，寒假作业就像没嚼劲的鱿鱼干一样好办！@啊哈哈！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":101}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":100300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":200}]}],"group_22":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_52_30","textHome":"在值得庆贺的新年里就想威胁神滨的和平，最@强的由比鹤乃绝不容许！尽管放马过来吧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":201}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":100300,"motion":200}]}],"group_23":[{"autoTurnFirst":7.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_52_31","textHome":"难道说，无尽镜界里的复制品们也在享受新年@的假期吗!?诶诶，一起去看看情况吧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":101}]}],"group_24":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_52_32","textHome":"嘛，这里就交给我吧！我可是以一当十！鹤乃@的力量可是谁来都一样炸飞的，认命吧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":101}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":100300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":201}]}],"group_25":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_52_33","textHome":"好想赶紧吃到中华年糕啊！今年的刚刚做出来@，虽然我还没吃，但想想就很好吃！还可以@用芝麻油来炸！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":101}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":100}]}],"group_26":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":101,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_52_34","textHome":"年夜饭是寄托着愿望的哦。「就像炒饭里的米@粒一样，一整年都油光发亮」这样的！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.9,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":100300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":100}]}],"group_27":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_52_35","textHome":"呼——开年就有好工作！正在教莎奈和菲莉希@亚鹤乃流・转陀螺的秘诀！两人一定会成为@一把好手的！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.2,"chara":[{"id":100300,"motion":201}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":100300,"motion":0}]}],"group_28":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_52_36","textHome":"哪怕是长袖和服，也能做鹤乃体操！身体大幅@度向右转……再转！再转！向左转！再转！@腰部伸展运动！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.2,"chara":[{"id":100300,"motion":201}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":200}]}],"group_29":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_52_37","textHome":"嗯嗯!?鹤乃传感器有反应……！这是……嗯@，对！年糕小豆汤的香味！原来如此，香味@的来源是三日月别墅。好，那就去吧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":201}]}],"group_3":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_00_04","textHome":"接下来才是更加刻苦的修行，@我要成为首屈一指的魔法少女！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":100}]}],"group_30":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_10